'''[http://cashwiki.org Cashwiki]''' is a collaborative website about money. It is started from texts available under the GFDL or in the public domain. It was created by [[User:Guaka|Guaka]] on September 20th, 2008.

Guaka has worked on many non-profit community wikis since 2003 and decided to try to make some money with the skills acquired. After starting trashwiki.org, Cashwiki was the logical next step, a collaborative website to gather information on how to make money, to supercede money.

In the beginning texts will be copied from various sources, such as Wikipedia, Wikibooks and Finwikian. The course of time will decide where we'll go. Guaka's preference goes to [[:Category:Money|P2P-style ideas]].

There are some ads - though feel very free to create an account and change to an ad-less skin. 

